    <small>Software Craftsman (Developer)</small>
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>
        Andrew's hunger for knowledge and determination to turn 
        information into action has contributed to his most recent 
        success at Vabrise Technologies. There, he led a team of 
        developers in creating outstanding websites for organisations 
        such as Kakamega CSO Network. He considers himself a `forever 
        student`, eager to build learn daily. Meanwhile, he is currently 
        undergoing a six month software engineering training at Moringa 
        School with the aim of better honing his skills in the software 
        world. He also believes that mindfulness in the workplace is key 
        to success, a tenet he lives out through his interests in yoga, 
        meditation, biking, and having nature walks. 
